{"title":"军营组诗","authors":["中士　谢礼标"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"军营组诗\t中士　谢礼标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜炮上坐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜黑漆漆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像口大黑锅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帐篷里面静悄悄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高射炮兵炮上坐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞贼嗡嗡叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全身打哆嗦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偷偷窜到海防线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想进大陆撒罪恶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士盯着眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒火上心窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长一声命令下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山摇地动满天火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌机被打中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧成老蛤蟆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掉入海里喂王八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条毒蛇下油锅……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们入梦乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士炮上坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国领空最神圣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖魔鬼怪逃不脱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慰问信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我守卫在南海边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫美丽的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接到亲人的慰问信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张张是激情的诗篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自人民公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自工厂车间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰产田里的勇士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织布机旁的姑娘……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那豪迈的语句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像波涛在喧响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心血在沸腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身充满力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用粗大的双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把武器擦亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那雄伟的炮口啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫着天空和海洋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜的灯光……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我挎上冲锋枪走出营房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接下了午夜的流动岗哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们都在被窝里做着甜梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王团长的窗口还亮着灯光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我轻轻地走近玻璃窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴着玻璃向里面张望——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哟，王团长在学代数哪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟蒂把桌上的烟碟塞满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他那满额的皱纹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记载着走过的路程；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他那斑白的头发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历过多少时代的风霜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，他又用刚强的毅力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向文化科学宣战！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的心是一堆不灭的篝火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像这深夜的灯光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在云涛里巡逻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机场散发油香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马达日夜喧响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾驶着国产的雄鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞入苍茫的蓝天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚披上北方的梅花雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又闻到南国的椰林香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚踏上东海的滔天浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又冲过西南的高山巅……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛穿透密密层云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云里霹雷日夜轰响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸手撒下满天鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国到处是和平的春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在云涛里巡逻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长空挂在心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个空域就是一个哨位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条云缝就是一个枪眼！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}